title: 06/25/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 06/25/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP is joined by Suns' analyst Eddie Johnson to recap last night's game. How much of an effect did the mask have on Devin Booker? Pro Football Talk's Steve Palazzolo explains why Pro Football focus has Josh Allen ranked 40th. And Todd throws down the gauntlet in the first annual limerick-off.
